OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FHeavy and
OL,6,Fthundery showers continuing this
OL,7,Fevening, with some sunny interludes.
OL,8,FDrier conditions to follow overnight
OL,9,Fas showers gradually fade. A chilly
OL,10,Fnight especially in rural spots.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FA dry start for most on
OL,13,FWednesday with sunny spells in the
OL,14,Fmorning. Showers developing from late
OL,15,Fmorning, these may be heavy and turn
OL,16,Fthundery by the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
