OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FA
OL,6,Fband of rain moves in Thursday
OL,7,Fmorning, turning drier by the evening.
OL,8,FLargely fine and dry Friday and
OL,9,FSaturday. Temperatures above average
OL,10,Fby the weekend.
